content:
It's December again! That means we're prepping for our 8th annual state of the "log" episode and we need your help! Go here:

https://changelog.fm/sotl

And leave us a message. If your audio is used on the show, we'll hook you up with your very own Breakmaster Cylinder remix! :dancing:
Sent mine in, earlier than my usual last minute (or well past editing window) :joy:

Thanks, Jamie!

Come on, y'all! We still need MOAR voicemails! :pray:
Speaking of state of the log... it'd be fun to see what's the episode with the "longest running" discussion based on its Zulip thread?
Off the top of my head I’m going to guess it was the distributed AI episode. That one got… lively. :joy:
This is my homework for tonight :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes:
From what I can remember, that Wordpress drama thread was the longest.
Oh yeah I bet. Not an episode but surely deserves a (dis)honourable mention!
I noticed that the first episode of this year talks about predictions. It would be cool to take about what was right and what was off :smiley:
When's this out? Is it this week?
